          "message": {
            "text": "Hardcoded model name: '\n    Sync SharkRouter client — drop-in replacement for openai.OpenAI.\n\n    Usage:\n        client = SharkSyncClient(\n            api_key=\"sk-shark-...\",\n            user_id=\"user-123\",\n        )\n\n        response = client.chat.completions.create(\n            model=\"gpt-4o\",\n            messages=[{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello\"}],\n        )\n\n    Same header injection guarantees as SharkClient (async version).\n    ' — no routing/fallback"
          },
